{"tid":911494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"替死鬼 【馬拉松遞國旗  主辦方：這是禮遇】","createTime":"2018-11-22T03:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T03:49:52.000Z","uid":74778,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0367bb52f8f59b6e368166fbeab940c57bb8f55e","tid":911494,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"【馬拉松遞國旗  主辦方：這是禮遇】<br />\n<br />\n蘇州馬拉松義工在跑道遞國旗予中國選手，主辦方智美體育負責人指「遞國旗是慣例，是對選手的禮遇及尊重」，形容披著國旗衝線可以表達對國家培養的感謝，場面震撼。但他強調披國旗是自願，不是強迫。他指今次是義工接到指示後，沒有靈活把握，沒考慮到選手當時分秒必爭，是無心之過，但指未來遞國旗安排不會變。<br />\n<br />\n#蘇州馬拉松<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1946970032114140/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1946970032114140%2F&d=Z5iWXm4WO3jE20R3F9d1rsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=4f28883f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1946970032114140/</a>"},{"pid":"11c66e735bedc3ea51f49e92df55de4763ee0fbe","tid":911494,"uid":126100,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"支那 logic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  撚尻你係禮遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cc4ab8f079c0ebdb2e3312be1c8a9e40d4472d","tid":911494,"uid":2949,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"白事又成功變紅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0332e10134f9059f73b2cd98be2042d78e99e2d1","tid":911494,"uid":28599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T03:11:31.000Z","msg":"失敗係個人<br />\n榮耀係國家"},{"pid":"18b70fb2bdb346b9de33fb23d4d7a44cd6217f16","tid":911494,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30cc4ab8f079c0ebdb2e3312be1c8a9e40d4472d","tid":911494,"uid":2949,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"白事又成功變紅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/no